<~>are<~>known<~>correctly<~>,<~>just<~>like<~>the<~>*NL*<~>particular<~>present<~>;<~>but<~>there<~>are<~>gaps<~>in<~>their<~>recollection<~>which<~>they<~>*NL*<~>fill<~>up<~>with<~>fictions<~>,<~>and<~>these<~>are<~>either<~>always<~>the<~>same<~>,<~>in<~>which<~>case<~>*NL*<~>they<~>become<~>fixed<~>ideas<~>,<~>and<~>the<~>madness<~>that<~>results<~>is<~>called<~>monomania<~>*NL*<~>or<~>melancholy<~>;<~>or<~>they<~>are<~>always<~>different<~>,<~>momentary<~>fancies<~>,<~>and<~>then<~>*NL*<~>it<~>is<~>called<~>folly<~>,<~>fatuitas<~>.<~>This<~>is<~>why<~>it<~>is<~>so<~>difficult<~>to<~>find<~>out<~>*NL*<~>their<~>former<~>life<~>from<~>lunatics<~>when<~>they<~>enter<~>an<~>asylum<~>.<~>The<~>true<~>and<~>*NL*<~>the<~>false<~>are<~>always<~>mixed<~>up<~>in<~>their<~>memory<~>.<~>Although<~>the<~>immediate<~>*NL*<~>present<~>is<~>correctly<~>known<~>,<~>it<~>becomes<~>falsified<~>through<~>its<~>fictitious<~>*NL*<~>connection<~>with<~>an<~>imaginary<~>past<~>;<~>they<~>therefore<~>regard<~>themselves<~>and<~>*NL*<~>others<~>as<~>identical<~>with<~>persons<~>who<~>exist<~>only<~>in<~>their<~>imaginary<~>past<~>;<~>*NL*<~>they<~>do<~>not<~>recognise<~>some<~>of<~>their<~>acquaintances<~>at<~>all<~>,<~>and<~>thus<~>while<~>*NL*<~>they<~>perceive<~>correctly<~>what<~>is<~>actually<~>present<~>,<~>they<~>have<~>only<~>false<~>*NL*<~>conceptions<~>of<~>its<~>relations<~>to<~>what<~>is<~>absent<~>.<~>If<~>the<~>madness<~>reaches<~>a<~>*NL*<~>high<~>degree<~>,<~>there<~>is<~>complete<~>absence<~>of<~>memory<~>,<~>so<~>that<~>the<~>madman<~>is<~>*NL*<~>quite<~>incapable<~>of<~>any<~>reference<~>to<~>what<~>is<~>absent<~>or<~>past<~>,<~>and<~>is<~>only<~>*NL*<~>determined<~>by<~>the<~>caprice<~>of<~>the<~>moment<~>in<~>connection<~>with<~>the<~>fictions<~>*NL*<~>which<~>,<~>in<~>his<~>mind<~>,<~>fill<~>the<~>past<~>.<~>In<~>such<~>a<~>case<~>,<~>we<~>are<~>never<~>for<~>a<~>*NL*<~>moment<~>safe<~>from<~>violence<~>or<~>murder<~>,<~>unless<~>we<~>constantly<~>make<~>the<~>madm