unequal<~>weight<~>and<~>consistency<~>,<~>but<~>not<~>*NL*<~>distinguishable<~>to<~>the<~>eye<~>,<~>the<~>whole<~>building<~>would<~>become<~>as<~>utterly<~>*NL*<~>incapable<~>of<~>affording<~>us<~>pleasure<~>as<~>a<~>poem<~>in<~>an<~>unknown<~>language<~>.<~>All<~>*NL*<~>this<~>proves<~>that<~>architecture<~>does<~>not<~>affect<~>us<~>mathematically<~>,<~>but<~>also<~>*NL*<~>dynamically<~>,<~>and<~>that<~>what<~>speaks<~>to<~>us<~>through<~>it<~>,<~>is<~>not<~>mere<~>form<~>and<~>*NL*<~>symmetry<~>,<~>but<~>rather<~>those<~>fundamental<~>forces<~>of<~>nature<~>,<~>those<~>first<~>*NL*<~>Ideas<~>,<~>those<~>lowest<~>grades<~>of<~>the<~>objectivity<~>of<~>will<~>.<~>The<~>regularity<~>of<~>*NL*<~>the<~>building<~>and<~>its<~>parts<~>is<~>partly<~>produced<~>by<~>the<~>direct<~>adaptation<~>of<~>*NL*<~>each<~>member<~>to<~>the<~>stability<~>of<~>the<~>whole<~>,<~>partly<~>it<~>serves<~>to<~>facilitate<~>*NL*<~>the<~>survey<~>and<~>comprehension<~>of<~>the<~>whole<~>,<~>and<~>finally<~>,<~>regular<~>figures<~>to<~>*NL*<~>some<~>extent<~>enhance<~>the<~>beauty<~>because<~>they<~>reveal<~>the<~>constitution<~>of<~>*NL*<~>space<~>as<~>such<~>.<~>But<~>all<~>this<~>is<~>of<~>subordinate<~>value<~>and<~>necessity<~>,<~>and<~>by<~>*NL*<~>no<~>means<~>the<~>chief<~>concern<~>;<~>indeed<~>,<~>symmetry<~>is<~>not<~>invariably<~>demanded<~>,<~>*NL*<~>as<~>ruins<~>are<~>still<~>beautiful<~>.<~>*NL*<~>*NL*<~>Works<~>of<~>architecture<~>have<~>further<~>quite<~>a<~>special<~>relation<~>to<~>light<~>;<~>they<~>*NL*<~>gain<~>a<~>double<~>beauty<~>in<~>the<~>full<~>sunshine<~>,<~>with<~>the<~>blue<~>sky<~>as<~>a<~>*NL*<~>background<~>,<~>and<~>again<~>they<~>have<~>quite<~>a<~>different<~>effect<~>by<~>moonlight<~>.<~>*NL*<~>Therefore<~>,<~>when<~>a<~>beautiful<~>work<~>of<~>architecture<~>is<~>to<~>be<~>erected<~>,<~>special<~>*NL*<~>attention<~>is<~>always<~>paid<~>to<~>the<~>effects<~>of<~>the<~>light<~>and<~>to<~>the<~>climate<~>.<~>*NL*<~>The<~>reason<~>of<~>all<~>this<~>is<~>,<