*NL*<~>the<~>pure<~>subject<~>of<~>knowing<~>free<~>from<~>will<~>.<~>It<~>will<~>consist<~>then<~>*NL*<~>principally<~>in<~>pure<~>contemplation<~>itself<~>,<~>free<~>from<~>all<~>the<~>suffering<~>of<~>*NL*<~>will<~>and<~>of<~>individuality<~>.<~>In<~>this<~>respect<~>the<~>opposite<~>of<~>architecture<~>,<~>*NL*<~>and<~>the<~>other<~>extreme<~>of<~>the<~>series<~>of<~>the<~>fine<~>arts<~>,<~>is<~>the<~>drama<~>,<~>which<~>*NL*<~>brings<~>to<~>knowledge<~>the<~>most<~>significant<~>Ideas<~>.<~>Therefore<~>in<~>the<~>æsthetic<~>*NL*<~>pleasure<~>afforded<~>by<~>the<~>drama<~>the<~>objective<~>side<~>is<~>throughout<~>*NL*<~>predominant<~>.<~>*NL*<~>*NL*<~>Architecture<~>has<~>this<~>distinction<~>from<~>plastic<~>art<~>and<~>poetry<~>:<~>it<~>does<~>not<~>*NL*<~>give<~>us<~>a<~>copy<~>but<~>the<~>thing<~>itself<~>.<~>It<~>does<~>not<~>repeat<~>,<~>as<~>they<~>do<~>,<~>the<~>*NL*<~>known<~>Idea<~>,<~>so<~>that<~>the<~>artist<~>lends<~>his<~>eyes<~>to<~>the<~>beholder<~>,<~>but<~>in<~>it<~>*NL*<~>the<~>artist<~>merely<~>presents<~>the<~>object<~>to<~>the<~>beholder<~>,<~>and<~>facilitates<~>for<~>*NL*<~>him<~>the<~>comprehension<~>of<~>the<~>Idea<~>by<~>bringing<~>the<~>actual<~>,<~>individual<~>*NL*<~>object<~>to<~>a<~>distinct<~>and<~>complete<~>expression<~>of<~>its<~>nature<~>.<~>*NL*<~>*NL*<~>Unlike<~>the<~>works<~>of<~>the<~>other<~>arts<~>,<~>those<~>of<~>architecture<~>are<~>very<~>seldom<~>*NL*<~>executed<~>for<~>purely<~>æsthetic<~>ends<~>.<~>These<~>are<~>generally<~>subordinated<~>to<~>*NL*<~>other<~>useful<~>ends<~>which<~>are<~>foreign<~>to<~>art<~>itself<~>.<~>Thus<~>the<~>great<~>merit<~>of<~>*NL*<~>the<~>architect<~>consists<~>in<~>achieving<~>and<~>attaining<~>the<~>pure<~>æsthetic<~>ends<~>,<~>*NL*<~>in<~>spite<~>of<~>their<~>subordination<~>to<~>other<~>ends<~>which<~>are<~>foreign<~>to<~>them<~>.<~>*NL*<~>This<~>he<~>does<~>by<~>cleverly<~>adapting<~>them<~>in<~>a<~>variety<~>of<~>ways<~>to<~>the<~>*NL*<~>arbitrary<~>ends<~>in<~>view<~>,<~>and<~>