>the<~>want<~>of<~>this<~>that<~>prevents<~>another<~>art<~>from<~>taking<~>its<~>*NL*<~>place<~>beside<~>architecture<~>as<~>a<~>sister<~>art<~>,<~>although<~>in<~>an<~>æsthetical<~>point<~>*NL*<~>of<~>view<~>it<~>is<~>quite<~>properly<~>to<~>be<~>classed<~>along<~>with<~>it<~>as<~>its<~>*NL*<~>counterpart<~>;<~>I<~>mean<~>artistic<~>arrangements<~>of<~>water<~>.<~>For<~>what<~>architecture<~>*NL*<~>accomplishes<~>for<~>the<~>Idea<~>of<~>gravity<~>when<~>it<~>appears<~>in<~>connection<~>with<~>*NL*<~>that<~>of<~>rigidity<~>,<~>hydraulics<~>accomplishes<~>for<~>the<~>same<~>Idea<~>,<~>when<~>it<~>is<~>*NL*<~>connected<~>with<~>fluidity<~>,<~>i.e.<~>,<~>formlessness<~>,<~>the<~>greatest<~>mobility<~>and<~>*NL*<~>transparency<~>.<~>Leaping<~>waterfalls<~>foaming<~>and<~>tumbling<~>over<~>rocks<~>,<~>*NL*<~>cataracts<~>dispersed<~>into<~>floating<~>spray<~>,<~>springs<~>gushing<~>up<~>as<~>high<~>*NL*<~>columns<~>of<~>water<~>,<~>and<~>clear<~>reflecting<~>lakes<~>,<~>reveal<~>the<~>Ideas<~>of<~>fluid<~>*NL*<~>and<~>heavy<~>matter<~>,<~>in<~>precisely<~>the<~>same<~>way<~>as<~>the<~>works<~>of<~>architecture<~>*NL*<~>unfold<~>the<~>Ideas<~>of<~>rigid<~>matter<~>.<~>Artistic<~>hydraulics<~>,<~>however<~>,<~>obtains<~>no<~>*NL*<~>support<~>from<~>practical<~>hydraulics<~>,<~>for<~>,<~>as<~>a<~>rule<~>,<~>their<~>ends<~>can<~>not<~>be<~>*NL*<~>combined<~>;<~>yet<~>,<~>in<~>exceptional<~>cases<~>,<~>this<~>happens<~>;<~>for<~>example<~>,<~>in<~>the<~>*NL*<~>Cascata<~>di<~>Trevi<~>at<~>Rome<~>.<~>-LRB-<~>52<~>-RRB-<~>*NL*<~>*NL*<~>§<~>44<~>.<~>What<~>the<~>two<~>arts<~>we<~>have<~>spoken<~>of<~>accomplish<~>for<~>these<~>lowest<~>*NL*<~>grades<~>of<~>the<~>objectivity<~>of<~>will<~>,<~>is<~>performed<~>for<~>the<~>higher<~>grades<~>of<~>*NL*<~>vegetable<~>nature<~>by<~>artistic<~>horticulture<~>.<~>The<~>landscape<~>beauty<~>of<~>a<~>scene<~>*NL*<~>consists<~>,<~>for<~>the<~>most<~>part<~>,<~>in<~>the<~>multiplicity<~>of<~>natural<~>objects<~>which<~>*NL*<~>are<~>present<~>