<~>this<~>is<~>that<~>animals<~>*NL*<~>have<~>only<~>the<~>character<~>of<~>their<~>species<~>,<~>no<~>individual<~>character<~>.<~>In<~>the<~>*NL*<~>representation<~>of<~>men<~>the<~>character<~>of<~>the<~>species<~>is<~>separated<~>from<~>that<~>*NL*<~>of<~>the<~>individual<~>;<~>the<~>former<~>is<~>now<~>called<~>beauty<~>-LRB-<~>entirely<~>in<~>the<~>*NL*<~>objective<~>sense<~>-RRB-<~>,<~>but<~>the<~>latter<~>retains<~>the<~>name<~>,<~>character<~>,<~>or<~>*NL*<~>expression<~>,<~>and<~>the<~>new<~>difficulty<~>arises<~>of<~>representing<~>both<~>,<~>at<~>once<~>*NL*<~>and<~>completely<~>,<~>in<~>the<~>same<~>individual<~>.<~>*NL*<~>*NL*<~>Human<~>beauty<~>is<~>an<~>objective<~>expression<~>,<~>which<~>means<~>the<~>fullest<~>*NL*<~>objectification<~>of<~>will<~>at<~>the<~>highest<~>grade<~>at<~>which<~>it<~>is<~>knowable<~>,<~>the<~>*NL*<~>Idea<~>of<~>man<~>in<~>general<~>,<~>completely<~>expressed<~>in<~>the<~>sensible<~>form<~>.<~>But<~>*NL*<~>however<~>much<~>the<~>objective<~>side<~>of<~>the<~>beautiful<~>appears<~>here<~>,<~>the<~>*NL*<~>subjective<~>side<~>still<~>always<~>accompanies<~>it<~>.<~>And<~>just<~>because<~>no<~>object<~>*NL*<~>transports<~>us<~>so<~>quickly<~>into<~>pure<~>æsthetic<~>contemplation<~>,<~>as<~>the<~>most<~>*NL*<~>beautiful<~>human<~>countenance<~>and<~>form<~>,<~>at<~>the<~>sight<~>of<~>which<~>we<~>are<~>*NL*<~>instantly<~>filled<~>with<~>unspeakable<~>satisfaction<~>,<~>and<~>raised<~>above<~>ourselves<~>*NL*<~>and<~>all<~>that<~>troubles<~>us<~>;<~>this<~>is<~>only<~>possible<~>because<~>this<~>most<~>distinct<~>*NL*<~>and<~>purest<~>knowledge<~>of<~>will<~>raises<~>us<~>most<~>easily<~>and<~>quickly<~>to<~>the<~>*NL*<~>state<~>of<~>pure<~>knowing<~>,<~>in<~>which<~>our<~>personality<~>,<~>our<~>will<~>with<~>its<~>*NL*<~>constant<~>pain<~>,<~>disappears<~>,<~>so<~>long<~>as<~>the<~>pure<~>æsthetic<~>pleasure<~>lasts<~>.<~>*NL*<~>Therefore<~>it<~>is<~>that<~>Goethe<~>says<~>:<~>``<~>No<~>evil<~>can<~>touch<~>him<~>who<~>looks<