us<~>away<~>from<~>desire<~>.<~>Therefore<~>,<~>in<~>the<~>*NL*<~>lyric<~>and<~>the<~>lyrical<~>mood<~>,<~>desire<~>-LRB-<~>the<~>personal<~>interest<~>of<~>the<~>ends<~>-RRB-<~>,<~>*NL*<~>and<~>pure<~>perception<~>of<~>the<~>surrounding<~>presented<~>,<~>are<~>wonderfully<~>mingled<~>*NL*<~>with<~>each<~>other<~>;<~>connections<~>between<~>them<~>are<~>sought<~>for<~>and<~>imagined<~>;<~>the<~>*NL*<~>subjective<~>disposition<~>,<~>the<~>affection<~>of<~>the<~>will<~>,<~>imparts<~>its<~>own<~>hue<~>to<~>*NL*<~>the<~>perceived<~>surrounding<~>,<~>and<~>conversely<~>,<~>the<~>surroundings<~>communicate<~>*NL*<~>the<~>reflex<~>of<~>their<~>colour<~>to<~>the<~>will<~>.<~>The<~>true<~>lyric<~>is<~>the<~>expression<~>*NL*<~>of<~>the<~>whole<~>of<~>this<~>mingled<~>and<~>divided<~>state<~>of<~>mind<~>.<~>In<~>order<~>to<~>make<~>*NL*<~>clear<~>by<~>examples<~>this<~>abstract<~>analysis<~>of<~>a<~>frame<~>of<~>mind<~>that<~>is<~>very<~>*NL*<~>far<~>from<~>all<~>abstraction<~>,<~>any<~>of<~>the<~>immortal<~>songs<~>of<~>Goethe<~>may<~>be<~>*NL*<~>taken<~>.<~>As<~>specially<~>adapted<~>for<~>this<~>end<~>I<~>shall<~>recommend<~>only<~>a<~>few<~>:<~>*NL*<~>``<~>The<~>Shepherd<~>'s<~>Lament<~>,<~>''<~>``<~>Welcome<~>and<~>Farewell<~>,<~>''<~>``<~>To<~>the<~>Moon<~>,<~>''<~>``<~>On<~>the<~>*NL*<~>Lake<~>,<~>''<~>``<~>Autumn<~>;<~>''<~>also<~>the<~>songs<~>in<~>the<~>``<~>Wunderhorn<~>''<~>are<~>excellent<~>*NL*<~>examples<~>;<~>particularly<~>the<~>one<~>which<~>begins<~>,<~>``<~>O<~>Bremen<~>,<~>I<~>must<~>now<~>leave<~>*NL*<~>thee<~>.<~>''<~>As<~>a<~>comical<~>and<~>happy<~>parody<~>of<~>the<~>lyrical<~>character<~>a<~>song<~>of<~>*NL*<~>Voss<~>strikes<~>me<~>as<~>remarkable<~>.<~>It<~>describes<~>the<~>feeling<~>of<~>a<~>drunk<~>plumber<~>*NL*<~>falling<~>from<~>a<~>tower<~>,<~>who<~>observes<~>in<~>passing<~>that<~>the<~>clock<~>on<~>the<~>tower<~>*NL*<~>is<~>at<~>half-past<~>eleven<~>,<~>a<~>remark<~>which<~>is<~>quite<~>foreign<~>to<~>his<~>condition<~>,<~>*NL*<~>and<~>thu